I remember this day still so clearly. Art and I worked for OPIE instructional television in Oxnard. So many classrooms filled with space enthused students and teachers watching the launch of the first teacher in space, Christa McAuliffe. I will never forget the shock of what soon happened. I prayed the astronauts and the crew on board didn’t have time to realize what happened or suffer. I’ll never forget them.
